    <section class="project-head">
      <div class="container project-grid">
        <div class="project-copy">
          <div class="tag">Interior Project</div>
          <h1>Refined Harmony</h1>

          <p class="lead-en">A harmonious dialogue between cultures. This project pairs a soft, oat-toned aesthetic with a touch of European influence, shaping a calm interior language that feels both refined and deeply livable.</p>

          <p class="lead-zh">一場跨文化的和諧對話。此案以柔和的燕麥色調為基底，融入淡淡的歐式語彙，形塑出安靜、細緻且能被日常長時間感受的居住氛圍。</p>

          <p>The textures of dark brown and the organic veining of the green marble TV wall work together to mirror the landscape beyond the windows, blurring the line between indoors and out.</p>

          <p>Rather than relying on strong decorative gestures, the space is composed through tonal balance, material transitions, and measured proportions. Light, stone, wood, and shadow are arranged to create a setting that feels gentle, grounded, and quietly cohesive.</p>

          <p>深棕色材質的厚度與綠色大理石電視牆自然的紋理彼此呼應，像是將窗外景色的層次帶入室內，使空間與外部風景之間的界線變得柔和。</p>

          <p>整體設計並不依賴強烈裝飾，而是透過色調平衡、材質轉換與比例控制來建立空間節奏。光線、石材、木質與陰影被細緻安排，讓居住場景保有溫潤、沉穩且連續的感受。</p>
        </div>

        <aside class="project-meta">
          <div class="meta-item">
            <div class="meta-label">Dimensions</div>
            <div class="meta-value">133 sqm</div>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-item">
