    <section class="story">
      <div class="container story-grid">
        <div class="story-note">
          <div class="tag">Spatial Narrative</div>
          <h2>Material, view, and atmosphere</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="story-copy">
          <p>At the core of the project is the relationship between material softness and visual depth. Oat-toned finishes establish a calm base, while darker accents and stone surfaces introduce contrast without breaking the quiet overall mood.</p>

          <p>空間的核心在於柔和材質與視覺深度之間的關係。燕麥色系建立溫和底層，較深的色彩與石材表面則補足層次，使整體氛圍安靜卻不單薄。</p>

          <p>By framing views, preserving openness, and allowing textures to speak with restraint, the project seeks a balance between elegance and comfort — an interior that feels composed, but never distant.</p>

          <p>透過視線安排、開放感保留與克制的材料表現，這個空間希望在優雅與舒適之間取得平衡，讓居住感受保持細膩，同時不失親近性。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

