          <h2>Everyday calm in detail</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="story-copy">
          <p>Beyond the overall composition, the project is experienced through a sequence of quieter moments — the way light lands on surfaces, the transition between material textures, and the measured framing of furniture and circulation.</p>

          <p>除了整體構圖之外，這個空間真正的魅力也來自一連串較安靜的片刻：光線落在材質上的方式、不同表面之間的轉換，以及家具與動線被細緻安排後所形成的節奏。</p>

          <p>These views reveal how the project balances softness and structure. Rather than emphasizing singular focal points, the interior unfolds through layered details that support daily use while maintaining a refined visual atmosphere.</p>

          <p>這些畫面呈現了空間如何在柔和與秩序之間取得平衡。它並不依賴單一視覺焦點，而是透過層層細節累積出可被日常使用、也能被慢慢感受的生活場景。</p>
