            <p class="related-kicker">Related Object / Re:Craft</p>
            <h2 class="related-title">Green Top Side Table</h2>

            <p>The green tile surface of this object originates from the leftover Osaka tiles used on the TV wall in Refined Harmony, extending the material story of the interior into a smaller everyday piece.</p>

            <p>這件家具的綠色桌面，正是來自 Refined Harmony 電視牆鋪貼大阪磁磚後留下的剩餘材料，讓室內空間中的材質語言延伸成日常使用的物件。</p>

            <p>Rather than treating the remaining tiles as waste, the project repositions them as the starting point of a new object — one that carries the memory of the interior while entering a different scale of use.</p>

            <p>它並不是單純將剩料再次利用，而是把原本屬於空間表面的材料重新轉化，讓其在不同尺度中延續價值，也保留這個住宅案的材質記憶。</p>

